@startuml signup-email-verification-workspace-bootstrap
title Signup, Email Verification, and Workspace Bootstrap

hide footbox

skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam defaultFontSize 16
skinparam sequence {
  ArrowColor #111111
  LifeLineBorderColor #111111
  LifeLineBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
  ParticipantBorderColor #111111
  ParticipantBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
  ParticipantFontColor #111111
  ParticipantFontSize 16
  ActorBorderColor #111111
  ActorBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
  ActorFontSize 16
  GroupBorderColor #111111
  GroupBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
}

actor "New User" as User
participant "Signup UI" as UI
participant "Routes +\nValidation" as Routes
participant "Auth\nController" as Controller
participant "Auth\nService" as AuthService
participant "OTP + Email" as OtpEmail
participant "User/OTP\nmodels" as UserModels
participant "Workspace\nService" as WorkspaceService
participant "Workspace/Membership/\nMailbox/Billing models" as WorkspaceModels
participant "Session\nService" as SessionService
participant "Session model" as SessionModel

== 1. Signup request ==

User -> UI: Submit signup form
UI -> Routes: POST /api/auth/signup
Routes -> Controller: validated email/password/name
Controller -> AuthService: signup(email, password, name)
AuthService -> UserModels: create unverified user\nor reuse existing unverified user

== 2. Send verification OTP ==

AuthService -> OtpEmail: create verifyEmail OTP\nand send email fire-and-forget
OtpEmail -> UserModels: store hashed OTP with expiry
AuthService --> UI: success.auth.otpSent\n(no tokens yet)

== 3. Verify email ==

User -> UI: Submit OTP code
UI -> Routes: POST /api/auth/verify-email
Routes -> Controller: validated email/code/inviteToken?
Controller -> AuthService: verifyEmailAndLogin(email, code, inviteToken?)
AuthService -> OtpEmail: verify latest verifyEmail OTP
AuthService -> UserModels: mark email verified

== 4. Bootstrap workspace ==

alt Normal signup verification
  AuthService -> WorkspaceService: ensureWorkspaceForVerifiedUser(user)
  WorkspaceService -> WorkspaceModels: create owner workspace,\nowner membership, default mailbox
  WorkspaceService -> WorkspaceModels: create initial billing foundation\n(best effort)
else Verify with inviteToken
  AuthService -> WorkspaceService: ensureWorkspaceForVerifiedUser(user, inviteToken)
  WorkspaceService -> WorkspaceModels: validate invite, activate membership,\nmark invite accepted
  WorkspaceService -> WorkspaceModels: bootstrap default workspace\nonly if user has none
end

== 5. Create session tokens ==

WorkspaceService --> AuthService: active workspace context\n+ optional invite workspace context
AuthService -> SessionService: createSessionWithTokens(user, active workspace, role)
SessionService -> SessionModel: create session with refresh token hash
SessionService --> AuthService: accessToken + refreshToken
AuthService -> UserModels: update lastLoginAt
AuthService --> UI: success.auth.verified\nuser + tokens + workspace context

@enduml
